id: pm-web-rzmv
title: "Fix Daily Release: runs-on self-hosted has no registered runner, switch to ubuntu-latest"
description: "Daily Release runs queued 24h then auto-cancelled since 2026-06-10 (runs 27333897005, 27403423905): release.yml targets runs-on: self-hosted but the repo has zero self-hosted runners. All sibling pm packages release on ubuntu-latest. Switch to ubuntu-latest so the scheduled npm/GitHub release pipeline actually executes."
